modName: Quick Start - see  Intro to Console Commands on video
summary: This is a quick start with a level one character in Riverwood after escaping from Helgen.
descriptionHtml:
Th3e save game character starts as level 1 in Riverwood after escaping from Helgen.

The video at:   gives an intro into using the console commands to let you quickly build the character to enable more challenging game play and to remove some of the initial grind.
